      "anchor_refs": [
        "Berakhot 62b:11"
      ],
      "hebrew": "כִּ֣י תִשָּׂ֞א אֶת־רֹ֥אשׁ בְּנֵֽי־יִשְׂרָאֵל֮ לִפְקֻדֵיהֶם֒ וְנָ֨תְנ֜וּ אִ֣ישׁ כֹּ֧פֶר נַפְשׁ֛וֹ לַיהֹוָ֖ה בִּפְקֹ֣ד אֹתָ֑ם וְלֹא־יִהְיֶ֥ה בָהֶ֛ם נֶ֖גֶף בִּפְקֹ֥ד אֹתָֽם׃",
      "english": "When you take a census of the Israelites<sup class=\"footnote-marker\">b</sup><i class=\"footnote\"><b>Israelites </b>I.e., those qualified for the nation’s militia.</i> according to their army enrollment, each shall pay G<small>OD</small> a ransom for himself on being enrolled, that no plague may come upon them through their being enrolled.",
      "marker_line_index": 32,
      "placement_method": "quote_match",
      "placement_score": 77,
      "matched_snippet": "כי תשא את ראש בני ישראל לפקדיהם ונתנו איש כפר נפשו וגו",
      "source_kind": "direct_quote"
    },
    {
      "ref": "Genesis 32:3",
      "he_ref": "בראשית ל״ב:ג׳",
      "url": "https://www.sefaria.org/Genesis_32%3A3?lang=bi",
      "segment_ids": [
        14
      ],
      "anchor_refs": [
        "Berakhot 62b:15"
      ],
      "hebrew": "וַיֹּ֤אמֶר יַעֲקֹב֙ כַּאֲשֶׁ֣ר רָאָ֔ם מַחֲנֵ֥ה אֱלֹהִ֖ים זֶ֑ה וַיִּקְרָ֛א שֵֽׁם־הַמָּק֥וֹם הַה֖וּא מַֽחֲנָֽיִם׃&nbsp;<span class=\"mam-spi-pe\">{פ}</span><br>",
      "english": "When he saw them, Jacob said, “This is God’s camp.” So he named that place Mahanaim.<sup class=\"footnote-marker\">d</sup><i class=\"footnote\"><b>Mahanaim </b>Connected with Heb. <i>maḥaneh</i> “camp.”</i>",
      "marker_line_index": 38,
      "placement_method": "quote_match",
      "placement_score": 51,
      "matched_snippet": "ויאמר יעקב כאשר ראם",
      "source_kind": "direct_quote"
    },
    {
      "ref": "Genesis 22:8",
      "he_ref": "בראשית כ״ב:ח׳",
      "url": "https://www.sefaria.org/Genesis_22%3A8?lang=bi",
      "segment_ids": [
        14
      ],
      "anchor_refs": [
        "Berakhot 62b:15"
      ],
      "hebrew": "וַיֹּ֙אמֶר֙ אַבְרָהָ֔ם אֱלֹהִ֞ים יִרְאֶה־לּ֥וֹ הַשֶּׂ֛ה לְעֹלָ֖ה בְּנִ֑י וַיֵּלְכ֥וּ שְׁנֵיהֶ֖ם יַחְדָּֽו׃",
      "english": "And Abraham said, “It is God who will see to the sheep for this burnt offering, my son.” And the two of them walked on together.",
      "marker_line_index": 38,
      "placement_method": "quote_match",
      "placement_score": 12,
      "matched_snippet": "אלהים יראה לו השה",
      "source_kind": "direct_quote"
    },
    {
      "ref": "Exodus 30:16",
      "he_ref": "שמות ל׳:ט״ז",
      "url": "https://www.sefaria.org/Exodus_30%3A16?lang=bi",
