      "hebrew": "וַיָּב֕וֹא עַ֖ד לִפְנֵ֣י שַֽׁעַר־הַמֶּ֑לֶךְ כִּ֣י אֵ֥ין לָב֛וֹא אֶל־שַׁ֥עַר הַמֶּ֖לֶךְ בִּלְב֥וּשׁ שָֽׂק׃",
      "english": "until he came in front of the palace gate; for one could not enter the palace gate wearing sackcloth.—",
      "marker_line_index": 56,
      "placement_method": "quote_match",
